    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 欢迎来到 Arcane Afterfall – 一款受该类型经典启发的角色扮演游戏，在这里魔法不再统治，而那些渴望重现魔法的人必须为他们的目标而战。这是一个世界，人们从地球来到这里，寻找最后一滴魔法能量——却发现了新的谜团、古老的威胁，以及生存的斗争.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/ac954e6ff6f66d9c5d64ff4fa0277050.poster.avif?t=1769080675\" width=690 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/ac954e6ff6f66d9c5d64ff4fa0277050.webm?t=1769080675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/ac954e6ff6f66d9c5d64ff4fa0277050.mp4?t=1769080675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔍 探索一个充满阴谋与意外遭遇的神秘世界。加入秘密组织，破解谜题，并在最出乎意料的地方寻找稀有复活节彩蛋 🎭。在这里，每一次选择都会带来后果，而知识就是力量 📖✨.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战术战斗和致命敌人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 Arcane Afterfall 的战斗系统是为真正的策略家打造的。回合制战斗需要深思熟虑——使用独特技能 ⚡，组合天赋，分析敌人的弱点，发现漏洞 🎯，即使在最艰难的战斗中也能占据优势.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/e9448beb50b5b01e43d640f38f339a88.poster.avif?t=1769080675\" width=690 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/e9448beb50b5b01e43d640f38f339a88.webm?t=1769080675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/e9448beb50b5b01e43d640f38f339a88.mp4?t=1769080675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👹 但真正的考验在 boss 战中等待着你。巨大的恶魔 😈、被远古神器束缚的存在 🔮、以及机械巨人 🤖——每个 boss 都需要独特的策略。击败它们会给予你传奇奖励 🏆，但想要获胜，不仅要依靠力量，还得依赖智慧 🧠.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/6554c43aedaf56236266419991282c7c.poster.avif?t=1769080675\" width=690 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/6554c43aedaf56236266419991282c7c.webm?t=1769080675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/6554c43aedaf56236266419991282c7c.mp4?t=1769080675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>地下城、PVP  &quot;和奥术之塔&quot;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ 前往黑暗地牢探险——可以独自行动，也可以与队伍同行。每个迷宫都拥有自己的秘密与致命陷阱 ☠️，在深处则有强大的 boss 和宝藏 💎 等待着你。对于喜欢与其他玩家对抗的人来说，PvP 竞技场已经开放，你可以在团队对战 🏅 中测试自己的实力。而在 Tower of Arcana 中，你将从没有任何装备开始，并必须寻找各种方式赢得胜利——最终结果只取决于你的技巧.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/effa2338dca29c779aa227b825eb5dcd.poster.avif?t=1769080675\" width=690 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/effa2338dca29c779aa227b825eb5dcd.webm?t=1769080675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/effa2338dca29c779aa227b825eb5dcd.mp4?t=1769080675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一个充满神秘和可能性的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔮 穿透无名之城的 Inside Out，揭示它的秘密。挑战 Shaved Sisters 帮派，或者成为 Last Order 的圣骑士。加入 Swamp Legion 成为战士，或踏上探索 Zone 51 👽 的旅程。探究 Confluxion 中隐藏的奥秘，并穿上星辰运动鞋，在时空中找到属于自己的道路.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/13e8da8b28220d3a30401ad25034fc74.poster.avif?t=1769080675\" width=690 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/13e8da8b28220d3a30401ad25034fc74.webm?t=1769080675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220170/extras/13e8da8b28220d3a30401ad25034fc74.mp4?t=1769080675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcane Afterfall 永远不缺少可以去做的事——探索、战斗、解开谜题，并成为宏大故事的一部分!&quot;</p>",
